Function: avg_max_temp

Access the directory and get names of regions(table_name)
Do select query on tables and load desired data into pandas dataframe
Avg max temp for each region for every year will be stored in table with suffix {table_name}_avg_max_temp


Function: avg_min_temp

Access the directory and get names of regions(table_name)
Do select query on tables and load desired data into pandas dataframe
Avg min temp for each region for every year will be stored in table with suffix {table_name}_avg_min_temp

Function: total_accum_prec

Access the directory and get names of regions(table_name)
Do select query on tables and load desired data into pandas dataframe
total precipitation amount for each region for every year will be stored in table with suffix {table_name}_precipitation_amount
